OL,7,FThe UK is "sliding into an avoidable
OL,8,Fcrisis", the author of a major review
OL,9,Fon how to keep people in work has
OL,10,Fwarned as he urged a reduced reliance
OL,11,Fon fit notes amid an "enormous" cost
OL,12,Fto employers from ill health among
OL,13,Fworkers.
