OL,7,FPreviously published statistics show
OL,8,Fthat more than one in five working-age
OL,9,Fpeople are now out of work and not
OL,10,Flooking for work ` higher than many
OL,11,Fcomparator countries ` and that
OL,12,Fbringing the UK employment rate to 80%
OL,13,Fwould add two million people to the
OL,14,Fworkforce.
